summary: I think the reason Detective Pikachu works and is so far the best video game movie is that it doesn’t try to be anything but a...
body:
I think the reason Detective Pikachu works and is so far the best video game movie is that it doesn’t try to be anything but a Pokemon movie. It’s not trying to be dark or edgy, it’s not trying to be more adult, it’s just a Pokemon movie. And that makes it super enjoyable.

It reminded me of when I was a kid and how much I loved Pokemon. It reminded me a lot of the Pokemon movies I watched as a kid. It was cheesy at some parts but so what? Cheesiness is fun! 

It didn’t try to be something it wasn’t and I appreciated that.
